      • createPropertySource

        public PropertySource<?> createPropertySource(@Nullable
                                              java.lang.String name,
                                              EncodedResource resource)
                                       throws java.io.IOException
        从接口复制的说明: PropertySourceFactory
        Create a PropertySource that wraps the given resource.
        指定者:
        createPropertySource 在接口中 PropertySourceFactory
        参数:
        name - the name of the property source
        resource - the resource (potentially encoded) to wrap
        返回:
        the new PropertySource (never null)
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - if resource resolution failed
